text: Karma Tenzin (born 1 December 1972), is an archer who internationally represented Bhutan Tenzin competed for Bhutan at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona, he finished 71st in the individual event and the three man team finished 20th.Sports Reference Profile ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic archers of Bhutan Category:Archers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Bhutanese male archers
